<p><strike>out</strike> of the line &ndash; That is predicted for us at the end of this month &ndash; All other Divisions have had their month out on the Coast except ours so it is reasonable to expect that we shall get our turn &ndash; This being "shock" troops as we are called isn't bad, but rather interferes with one's period of rest as we might be pushed off to another part of the front at short notice -<br/>I am thinking of pushing for Paris leave should we get out &ndash; Most of our people have been &amp; a chance of seeing Paris in Spring is not to be sneezed at I'm told</p>
